        <li>Search</li>
    </ul>
    <p>A straightforward lookup with search criteria to narrow down the DB lookup.</p>
    <p>Again this uses Autocomplete to search the knowledge articles google style.</p>
    <p>The design I extracted fom an Apple Knowledge search gui I really liked the look of. I didn't copy any code, I just used Chrome F12 functions to analyse how the buttons were created using CSS and also the search field results view can be changed using the CSS controlled DIV buttons.</p>
